text: Typhoon Krosa, known in the Philippines as Typhoon Vinta was a Category 3 equivalent tropical cyclone that lashes the northern Philippines in Cagayan Valley region in October 2013 after the Typhoon Nari hits Central Luzon, Typhoon Krosa leaving atleast 4 deaths, and damaging houses nearby the coastal areas particularly in the town of Lal-lo, Cagayan. ==Meteorological== Krosa brought heavy rains and strong winds in the province of Cagayan. == See also == . * Typhoon Sarika * Typhoon Xangsane * Typhoon Usagi (2018) Category:2013 in weather Category:Pacific typhoons Category:2013 disasters in Asia
title: Typhoon Krosa (2013)
